# FULL SYSTEM WORKFLOW (UPDATED)

## Overview
This document describes the full workflow for:
- Customer registration and profiles
- Blogger request + approval system
- Blogger profiles (About + Avatar)
- Blog post publishing permissions
- Cart â†’ Booking system
- Admin role and approval responsibilities

---

## SYSTEM ACTORS
- **Guest (Unauthenticated User)**
- **Registered Customer**
- **Blogger (Approved User)**
- **Admin / CustomUser with elevated privileges**

---

